Above the translation is very wrong.  First, the pronoun &quot;he&quot; refers
to the Comforter because it is the nominative singular masculine
&quot;eikenos&quot; which requires a singular masculine antecedent.  Comforter
from the subsantive &quot;parakleton&quot; is nominative singular masculine and
